  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "krkORnvDrC5WL6fmgs6EGJm/MZw=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:38.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# object relations\n\nHow objects relate across the 21 document models in the Powerhouse ecosystem. The primary reference type is PHID for cross-model links and OID for intra-model references. See [[ecosystem map]] for the full model inventory organized by functional zone.\n\n## Cross-Model Hierarchy (Local Project)\n- [[five models form a hierarchy from facet through template to offering to subscription to instance]] \u2014 the core reference graph in this project's 5 models\n\n## Local Models (this project)\n- [[service-offering model defines tiered pricing with option groups and service groups]] \u2014 the central model with the most internal references (tiers \u2194 groups \u2194 services \u2194 options)\n- [[subscription-instance model tracks active customer subscriptions with lifecycle state]] \u2014 mirrors offering structure with billing actuals\n- [[resource-template model defines reusable service catalog blueprints]] \u2014 base catalog structure without pricing\n- [[resource-instance model tracks provisioned resource lifecycle]] \u2014 provisioned resource with facet configuration\n- [[facet model provides configurable classification dimensions]] \u2014 referenced by templates, offerings, and instances\n- [[service-subscription model tracks service-level subscription agreements]] \u2014 agreement-level subscription tracking\n\n## Cross-Zone References\n- [[builder-profile model describes individual contributor identities]] \u2014 SO.operatorId references this (Service & Pricing \u2192 Organization)\n- [[billing-statement model captures periodic billing summaries]] \u2014 SI produces billing statements (Service & Pricing \u2192 Finance)\n- [[invoice model generates formal payment requests]] \u2014 SI charges become invoice line items (Service & Pricing \u2192 Reporting)\n\n## Cross-Model Data Bridges\n- [[mapOfferingToSubscription transforms service offering state into subscription initialization]] \u2014 the primary offering \u2192 subscription bridge\n\n## Key Reference Patterns\n\n**PHID references (cross-model, local):**\n- `ServiceOffering.operatorId` \u2192 [[builder-profile model describes individual contributor identities]]\n- `ServiceOffering.resourceTemplateId` \u2192 ResourceTemplate\n- `SubscriptionInstance.serviceOfferingId` \u2192 ServiceOffering\n- `ResourceInstance.resourceTemplateId` \u2192 ResourceTemplate\n\n**PHID references (cross-zone):**\n- SubscriptionInstance \u2192 [[billing-statement model captures periodic billing summaries]]\n- SubscriptionInstance \u2192 [[invoice model generates formal payment requests]]\n- ScopeOfWork \u2192 [[builder-profile model describes individual contributor identities]] (assignees)\n- ScopeOfWork \u2192 [[invoice model generates formal payment requests]] (milestone billing)\n\n**OID references (intra-model):**\n- `Service.serviceGroupId` \u2192 ServiceGroup\n- `Service.optionGroupId` \u2192 OptionGroup\n- `ServiceGroupTierPricing.tierId` \u2192 Tier\n- `ServiceLevelBinding.serviceId` \u2192 Service\n- `ServiceUsageLimit.serviceId` \u2192 Service\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[index]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:38.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:38.000Z"
    }
  },
